英国说唱歌手和铁杆先驱MC Duke去世，58岁https://www.nme.com/music/uk-rapper-and-hardcore-pioneer-pioneer-mc-duke-duke-dies-58-3749852?utm_source=rsss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_medium = rsm_campaign=uk-rapper-rapper and-rapper-rapper-and-hardcore-pioneer- MC-Duke Dies-Aga-58Anagricel Duran Tue, 23 Apr 2024 17:03:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsHardcoreRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3749852 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NME新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “他的影响力在几代人中回荡，为我们今天所知道的充满活力的英国说唱界奠定了基础”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/music/uk-rapper-and-hardcore-pioneer-mc-duke-dies-age-58-3749852">英国邮政说唱歌手和铁杆先驱MC Duke去世，现年58岁，</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NME新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>英国说唱歌手Kashif Adham（也称为MC Duke）享年58岁。</p><p>郊区基本记录（Adham经常合作者之一）宣布了说唱歌手在其官方Instagram帐户上传递的消息。 “我们非常悲伤地分享了关于我们亲爱的朋友MC Duke去世的令人心碎的消息，”该职位开始说道。</p><p>它继续说：“自90年代初以来，我们有幸将他称为朋友和合作者，在我们郊区基地姐妹烙印（Boogie Times）上发行了最多的发行，目睹了他无与伦比的才华和对音乐的坚定奉献精神。 MC Duke巩固了他在英国音乐界的传奇地位。作为英国嘻哈的祖先，他的影响力在几代人中回荡，为我们今天所知道的充满活力的英国说唱界奠定了基础，我们希望许多人会在这个毁灭性的新闻上致敬。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6CLVB4Czbz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C